freetext.SYMPTOMS_DESCRIPTION: Since 1/23, I have experienced abdominal pain. I have had this in the past but it was controlled with omeprazole. I have had to double this and it has not resolved yet. Back and shoulder pain seem to be worse but opposite side of shot.
freetext.HEALTHCARE_VISITS_OTHER: Just doubled the medicine I already had

freetext.SYSTEMIC_REACTION_OTHER: I am not currently having any symptoms. The day after getting the shot, after filling out my v-safe survey, I felt slightly achy and temp of 99.3. It only lasted a few hours. Didnt require any medication. If forgot about it in my report yesterday.
Shins itching without a rash, some nasal allergy symptoms. Both are normal symptoms for me at times. Not sure if those are related, but I didn't have them before the shot.
This is normal for me. Does not feel out of the ordinary.
